OL,3,C'They thought I was dead': Boy injured
OL,4,Cin Gaza explosion lands in UK for
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FMajid al-Shagnobi requires major
OL,8,Ffacial reconstruction following the
OL,9,Fexplosion, as ITV News Correspondent
OL,10,FGeraint Vincent reports
OL,12,FA 15-year-old Palestinian boy who lost
OL,13,Fhis jaw and all of his teeth in an
OL,14,Fexplosion in Gaza is now being treated
OL,15,Fin the UK.
OL,17,FMajid al-Shagnobi suffered severe
OL,18,Ffacial injuries in February 2024 when
OL,19,FIsraeli tank shells exploded near him
OL,20,Fand a group of friends. He was trying
OL,21,Fto get humanitarian aid.
