OL,3,C'They thought I was dead': Boy injured
OL,4,Cin Gaza explosion lands in UK for
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FBefore Gaza's latest, most brutal war,
OL,8,FMajd was simply the eldest of four
OL,9,Fbrothers. Now, he's one of countless
OL,10,Fchildren caught in the crossfire of
OL,11,FIsrael and Hamas' conflict.
OL,13,FThe doctors in Gaza managed to save
OL,14,Fhis life - but only after they had
OL,15,Fdecided there was nothing they could
OL,16,Fdo.
