OL,3,C'They thought I was dead': Boy injured
OL,4,Cin Gaza explosion lands in UK for
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FSpeaking through a translator, Majd
OL,8,Ftold ITV News that when he first
OL,9,Farrived at the hospital, his injuries
OL,10,Fwere so severe that they thought he
OL,11,Fwas dead.
OL,13,F"I remember them putting me in the
OL,14,Fmortuary," Majd said.
OL,16,F"I managed to move my arm, though, and
OL,17,Fthey realised I was still alive."
