OL,3,C'They thought I was dead': Boy injured
OL,4,Cin Gaza explosion lands in UK for
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FEven after that, his mother, Islem
OL,8,FFelfel, recalls that doctors thought
OL,9,Fhis case was hopeless. They told her
OL,10,FMajd might only have days to live. One
OL,11,Fhospital refused to admit him.
OL,13,FBut now, Majd has a chance to fully
OL,14,Frestore his face, thanks to Project
OL,15,FPure Heart, a charity run by a group
OL,16,Fof healthcare professionals dedicated
OL,17,Fto bringing critically ill children
OL,18,Ffrom Middle East conflict zones to the
OL,19,FUK for treatment.
