OL,3,C'They thought I was dead': Boy injured
OL,4,Cin Gaza explosion lands in UK for
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FThey are using charitable donations to
OL,8,Fpay privately for the reconstructive
OL,9,Fsurgery Majd needs, and to house him,
OL,10,Fhis mum Islem, one of his brothers and
OL,11,Fhis little sister while they're here.
OL,13,FIslem speaks of the pride she has in
OL,14,Fthe courage her son has shown. But the
OL,15,Ftrauma for her family goes on.
OL,17,FTwo of her sons, Mohammad and Yusuf,
OL,18,Fremain in Gaza with their dad. It's
OL,19,Fdifficult for her to communicate with
OL,20,Fthem; she doesn't know if they have
OL,21,Fhad anything to eat today.
