OL,7,F"My heart is split between here and
OL,8,Fthere," she said.
OL,10,FMajd was flown into London on
OL,11,FWednesday night, but many other
OL,12,Fchildren in Gaza with critical
OL,13,Fconditions won't be so lucky.
OL,15,FOmar Din, a co-founder of Project Pure
OL,16,FHope, highlighted that the UK lags
OL,17,Fbehind European countries like Italy
OL,18,Fin taking children directly from Gaza.
OL,19,FMajd's family had to come through
OL,20,FEgypt.
