OL,7,FMr Din emphasised that the project is
OL,8,Fapolitical but said that the
OL,9,Fgovernment could do more "if they have
OL,10,Fthe will and they have the momentum".
OL,12,FMajd's family have a yearlong visa,
OL,13,Fwhich is meant to cover the time it
OL,14,Fwill take for him to undergo and
OL,15,Frecover from surgery. Then the charity
OL,16,Fplans to resettle them in Egypt or
OL,17,FJordan.
OL,19,FWhen ITV News asked Majd about what he
OL,20,Fhopes for now, he said simply to learn
OL,21,Fand to work.
